---
title: "Check Payment Status"
openapi: "POST /payment-links/status"
---

# Check Payment Status

This endpoint allows merchants to check the status of a payment using a unique transaction reference.

## Request Body

- **transactionReference** (string, required): The unique reference identifier for the payment transaction you want to check.

### Example Request

```json
{
  "transactionReference": "txn_123456789"
}
